    "• Comparative analysis: After AI produces content, students may be asked to compare it with human-created content on the same topic, identifying differences, similarities, and areas of divergence.",
    "This can include comparisons with human-generated content.",
    "• Critical evaluation: Students generate content with the express purpose of critiquing the output and questioning its choices, biases, and potential inaccuracies.",
    "• Integration: Students may be tasked with integrating AI-generated content into a larger project to ensure cohesion and alignment with broader objectives.",
    "This might constitute part of an industry project or part of an authentic assessment task."
  ],
